lue or ROI and management of product’s P&L. • Own product performance by setting success metrics and monitoring them to inform the future product roadmap. • Assess value, develop business cases, and prioritize items to ensure work focuses on those with maximum value that are aligned with product strategy. • Solicit, define and manage requirements for both internally and externally developed projects. • Oversees the creation, refinement and prioritization of the product backlog according to business and product strategy and set spring goals to contribute to the overall product vision. • Works closely with Development Leads and Scrum Masters to evaluate the product progress at the end of every sprint and accepts or rejects completed stories. • Understand, challenge and review technical design and architecture of the product and be tech curious. • Supports and holds accountable other supporting roles (such as sales, marketing, consulting, etc.) to the agreed deadlines and deliverables. • Writing test cases and running test campaigns. • Coordinate Business Implementation, UAD and leads review meetings to demonstrate enhancements/new features and obtain stakeholder signoffs. • Support product demonstrations, knowledge transfer and education. • Train the customer support and customer success teams on new capabilities in product releases. Profil recherché : Qualifications & Skills: • Master’s degree in software development, Computer Engineering, IT Project Management or related field. • 4+ years of experience in IT business analysis. • Fluent in English & French. • Curious, honest, ambitious and team oriented. • Likes to challenge and be challenged in return. Adresse de notre siège : Parc Casanearshore Sidi Maârouf Shore 14 Traits de personnalité souhaités : Implication au travail Besoin d\'autonomie Besoin de réflexion Ambition Recherche de nouveauté 4K Matching global N/A N/A FineTunePro COMPÉTENCES N/A Kapacity Revealer PERSONNALITÉ N/A Feel Good CULTURE Ici, vous pouve