evant leaders Responsible for the supervision and approval of dangerous operations in the jurisdiction, and confirm whether the operating conditions and personnel qualifications of the dangerous operations site meet the requirements Organize the area under jurisdiction to carry out hazard identification and evaluation, identify important risk factors, formulate control measures, and supervise the implementation Assisted in the \"three simultaneous\" work of the new EHS expansion in the responsible area, and organized the safety inspection before the commissioning of the new EHS expansion project in the responsible area Assist the Environmental Protection Department to supervise the compliance of three wastes (water, gas, slag) in the jurisdiction and the emergency treatment of environmental accidents Profil recherché : Able to speak English and French, and can communicate without obstacles in Morocco Manufacturing site safety and environmental management experience Skilled use of EXCEL, ppt, WORD and other office software Familiar with local EHS laws and regulations, as well as the company\'s internal EHS management flow Strong sense of responsibility, dedication, ability to help solve problems, strong ability to work under pressure Adresse de notre siège : Business Center EST étage 0 Anfa Place, bd de la corniche Traits de personnalité souhaités : Recherche de nouveauté Respect des règles Rationalisme Ténacité Besoin d\'objectivité Implication au travail Organisation 4K Matching global N/A N/A FineTunePro COMPÉTENCES N/A Kapacity Revealer PERSONNALITÉ N/A Feel Good CULTURE Ici, vous pouvez retrouver un taux de recommandation de cette offre pour vous, ainsi que des informations pour mettre en avant votre candidature. Connectez-vous / Inscrivez-vous pour consulter ces informations personnalisées. ReKrute vous offre ce nouveau test de personnalité pour mieux vous connaitre et valoriser vos candidatures. Passez-le dès maintenant, cela ne prend que 5 minutes maximum. Se