estion de projet, de la Finance et des Ressources Humaines, AXA GO Maroc soutient Group Operations dans la réalisation de sa mission. Poste : Role Description: You collaborate with Cyberark/Windows/Linux/Public cloud product teams, Group Security teams, Group Operation Security and other stakeholders . You serve as a technical security expert and as a security leader to senior management in the implementation and maintenance of security access model. Expertise Implementing Secure Systems: Security Architecture; Secure Development Information Assurance Methodologies and Testing Network Security: Architecture and secure implementation Incident Management: Incident Management; Investigation; Forensics Cyber Threat Management Audit, Assurance & Review: Audit & Review Your main tasks: Act as a main reference for security of Cyberark, contribute to the definition and extension of its Security Assurance Plan. Perform technical security tests, including replaying pentest intrusion scenarios from Red Teams. Interact with product experts and security teams to ensure the remediation of security vulnerabilities and security compliance. Analyze the exploitability of vulnerabilities in the context of a specific environment, weighting in the effect of various counter measures already in place (Firewall filtering rule reducing surface of expositions, EDR alerting systems, etc.) Any prior experience with security assessment of the following technologies is a plus: CyberArk, AWS, Active Directory, PingCastle, Windows, RedHat Linux, Palo Alto, EDR. Profil recherché : Profile: You hold a Bachelor/MSC degree in Computer Science, Engineering, or related field. You have more than 7 years experience in information security. Capacity to work in a matrix organization, driving tasks remotely and coordinate activities across the world. Skills / abilities Ability to learn quickly Ability to built own tools Strong interpersonal and communication skills; able to deal effectively with diverse cultures, skill sets and personalities, works effectively as a team player Organized with a proven ability to prioritize workload, meet deadlines, and utilize time effectively Operate comfortably at management level Strong facilitation, negotiation and conflict resolution skills Strong analytical skills Apply analytical rigor to understand complex vulnerabilities exploitation scenarios Fluent in French&English Adresse de notre siège : Technopolis Pôle Offshoring Rabat, Immeuble B2 Axa Traits de personnalité souhaités : Recherche de nouveauté Ambition Besoin de réflexion Besoin d\'autonomie Implication au travail 4K Matching global N/A N/A FineTunePro COMPÉTENCES N/A Kapacity Revealer PERSONNALITÉ N/A Feel Good CULTURE Ici, vous pouvez retrouver un taux de recommandation de cette offre pour vous, ainsi que des informations pour mettre en avant votre candidature. Connectez-vous / Inscrivez-vous pour consulter ces informations personnalisées. ReKrute vous offre ce nouveau test de personnalité pour mieux vous connaitre et valoriser vos candidatures. Passez-le dès maintenant, cela ne prend que 5 minutes maximum. Se connecter J\'utilise mon compte gmail Ou j\'utilise mon email Caps Lock Is On Rester connecté Mot de passe oublié ? Je me connecte Je m\'inscris Accueil Offres Conseils Entreprises × Technopolis Pôle Offshoring Rabat, Immeuble B2 Axa', 'https://www.rekrute.com/offre-emploi-tech-security-expert-recrutement-axa-group-operations-maroc-rabat-155983.html');
